## DVN SWORD v2 implementation

### DVN SWORD v2 implementation roadmap

- Still lots of work to do... so far it allows you to...
    - retrieve a SWORD service document after authenticating
    - create a study based on metadata (title, author, etc.) in an XML file, i.e. https://github.com/IQSS/dvn/blob/de603773c779a45f67b85908e8746b90c6e04661/tools/scripts/data-deposit-api/atom-entry-study.xml
- Next steps
    - after creating study, attach binary to it (2 step process is diagrammed at http://swordapp.org/2012/12/swordv2-compliance-how-to-achieve-it/ and described at http://www.mail-archive.com/sword-app-tech@lists.sourceforge.net/msg00327.html )
    - improve mapping between dcterms (Dublic Core) and DDI
    - merge https://github.com/IQSS/dvn/tree/3108-data-deposit-api into "develop" branch
    - deal with known bugs
        - start committing to https://github.com/IQSS/swordv2-java-server-library (bug fixes for https://github.com/swordapp/JavaServer2.0 )

### Merging branch into develop

DVN's SWORD implementation is being developed in this branch: https://github.com/IQSS/dvn/tree/3108-data-deposit-api 

Before merging, some talking points:

- Plan for using https://github.com/swordapp/JavaServer2.0 (sword2-server-1.0-classes.jar)
    - Known bugs
        - first character truncated from filename: https://github.com/swordapp/JavaServer2.0/pull/2
        - multipart deposit results in MalformedStreamException: https://github.com/dvn/swordpoc/issues/2
    - Fork repo under https://github.com/IQSS and submit pull requests?
    - Use Jenkins to build sword2-server-1.0-classes.jar? See https://help.hmdc.harvard.edu/Ticket/Display.html?id=162404
- URL patterns in servlet mappings: https://github.com/IQSS/dvn/blob/de603773c779a45f67b85908e8746b90c6e04661/src/DVN-web/web/WEB-INF/web.xml
    - `/api/data-deposit/swordv2/service-document/*`
    - `/api/data-deposit/swordv2/collection/*`
    - `/api/data-deposit/swordv2/edit/*`
- Many jars required (and more?):
    - abdera-core-1.1.1.jar
    - abdera-i18n-1.1.1.jar
    - abdera-parser-1.1.1.jar
    - axiom-api-1.2.10.jar
    - axiom-impl-1.2.10.jar
    - commons-fileupload-1.2.1.jar
    - sword2-server-1.0-classes.jar
    - xom-1.1.jar

